INSERT INTO activations (userId, serviceId, countryId, apiId, phoneNumber, status, smshubActivationId, createdAt)
SELECT 
  180002,
  1,
  1,
  2,
  CONCAT('+5511', LPAD(FLOOR(RAND() * 100000000), 8, '0')),
  'cancelled',
  FLOOR(RAND() * 1000000),
  DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL FLOOR(RAND() * 30) DAY)
FROM (SELECT 1 UNION SELECT 2 UNION SELECT 3 UNION SELECT 4 UNION SELECT 5 UNION SELECT 6) AS numbers
